  "_comment_architecture": [
    "WEEE end-of-life chain: collection (OBSERVE), sorting/inspection (OBSERVE),",
    "and recycling transformation (TransformationEvent).",
    "masterDataAvailableFor lists GS1 master data; the gs1: prefix is implicit and omitted inside the block.",
    "Extension properties (electronics:, dpp:) are at EVENT level.",
    "All ilmd blocks that previously sat on OBSERVE events have been moved to",
    "event-level extension properties; EPCIS 2.0 §7.3.8 forbids ilmd on OBSERVE.",
    "The recycling TransformationEvent's batch-level recovery-rate / carbon-offset",
    "data is observation-specific to THIS recycling run and therefore also rides",
    "at event level, not in ilmd.",
    "",
    "HTTP header: GS1-Extensions: dpp=https://ref.openepcis.io/extensions/common/core/,electronics=https://ref.openepcis.io/extensions/eu/electronics/",
    "See: extensions/common/core/docs/EPCIS_MASTERDATA_AND_EXTENSIONS.md",
    "GS1 demo prefix 952 (7-digit GCP: 9521234)."
  ],
